    <item>
      <title>美国就业率随工资增长而放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/world-economy-latest-us-employment-seen-moderating-along-with-wage-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[6 月份，美国雇主可能在工资增长放缓的同时减少了招聘，这对杰罗姆·鲍威尔及其美联储同事来说是一个有利的发展，他们正在寻求更多证据证明通胀正在放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/world-economy-latest-us-employment-seen-moderating-along-with-wage-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝丽尔升级为飓风，预计将“迅速”增强</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/hurricane-season-tropical-storm-beryl-will-threaten-caribbean</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国家飓风中心表示，2024 年大西洋飓风季的第二场热带风暴“贝里尔”已升级为飓风，并且“预计将迅速增强”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/hurricane-season-tropical-storm-beryl-will-threaten-caribbean</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 09:57:41 GMT</pubDate>
